\[|{\bf r}-{\bf r}'| = r-\frac{\bf{r} \cdot \bf{r}'}{r} + \cdots\]

<p>ã¨å±•é–‹ã§ãã¾ã™ã€‚ã“ã‚Œã‚ˆã‚Š</p>

\[T_{\mu \nu} ({\bf r}', t-\frac{|{\bf r}-{\bf r}'|}{c}) 
